hypui is an open source project provding Hybrid Proxy UI elements including:

hypcli - a RESTful command line interface to hypd.
hypweb - a RESTful web interface to hypd.

hypd is an implementation of a DNS Hybrid Proxy. See http://hypd.info for info.

The DNS Hybrid Proxy is an implementation of an Internet Draft standardized in the DNS-SD Working Group of the IETF.

The Internet Draft can be found here:

http://tools.ietf.org/html/draft-cheshire-dnssd-hybrid-01

More information about the DNS-SD Working group can be found here:

http://datatracker.ietf.org/wg/dnssd/
